def main():
    # input
    s = input().rstrip()
    t = input().rstrip()

    # initialization
    count = 0

    # count the number of characters different between s and t
    for i in range(len(s)):
        if s[i] != t[i]:
            count += 1

    # output
    print(count)

if __name__ == '__main__':
    main()
